node.text:
For today's walkthrough, here's our 20 ft. Homestead build for your enjoyment!

Want some nerdy specs? Here you go:

Specifications

Trailer: 20 ft. Trailer Made Custom Tiny Home Trailer Foundation
​Model: Mohican
Cost: Starting at $69,000
Exterior Siding: LP Vertical Smart Siding - 60 Year Warranty (With Aluminum Accent Panel)
Roof: Steel Roof - 40 Year Warranty
Exterior Storage Box: Included
Flooring: Luxury Vinyl Plank (LVP) Flooring
Interior Walls: Poplar Tongue & Groove
Hardware Package: Brushed Nickel Hardware Package
Social Area: Custom Bookcase & Open Space for Customer-Provided Furniture
Closet: Custom Shelving & Hanging Clothes Closet
Sleeping: Large King Loft
Stairs: Custom Staircase w/Built-In Storage

Kitchen

Cabinetry: Custom Cabinetry 
Backsplash: None
Countertops: Butcher Block
Sink: 30 In. Stainless Steel Undermount Sink
Oven/Range: None (Customer Provided)
Refrigerator: Apartment-Sized Stainless Steel Refrigerator
Microwave: None (Customer Provided)

Bathroom

Shower: Fiberglass Shower
Toilet: Nature's Head Composting Toilet
Shelving: Floating Shelves
Sink: None
Door: Custom Sliding Barn Door

Water/Heat/Insulation/Power

Heat/AC: Ductless Mini Split
Water Heater: Gas Propane Water Heater (PrecisionTemp)
Electric Service: 50 Amp Service w/Hybrid Power System for Solar
Insulation: Closed Cell Spray Foam Insulation: 3" In Walls/Ceilings, 4" In Floors

Like specifications like these? You can review all of the specs on our homes at www.moderntinyliving.com!

node.text:
Niagara, a 24 ft. tiny house based upon our Kokosing model, is today's glorious Walkthrough Wednsday!

If you've not enjoyed this beautiful home, take the next 2 minutes and give it look. Niagara features all of the amenities and features that make our Kokosing line one of the most popular modes in the world, but also includes a few design elements that really make it stick out. The extended work desk, for example, is a cusotm element that really make the home more usable for its owner.

Enjoy!

It's Walkthrough Wednesday!

This week's walkthrough comes to you on behalf of Serenity. Serenity is a 28 ft. custom tiny house on wheels by Modern Tiny Living. We shared the kitchen yesterday and figured it was high-time that we re-share the video walkthrough from last year!

Serenity is built similarly to one of our Point models, however it is extended 8 full feet, allowing for a much larger MTL social area as well as a full office suite in the rear of the unit (which includes its own entrance/exit).

Learn more at www.moderntinyliving.com/serenity

For today's #throwbackthursday, let's take a peak at our stunning modern shell. MTL's modern shell is the perfect canvas for the handy, aspiring DIY'er to build their dream tiny house.

Interested in a shell by MTL? Reach out to us directly at contact@moderntinyliving.com.

How to convert the MTL Social Area into a bed:

1. Remove cushions from the sides
2. Flip over the built in stands
3. Put cushions back on top of the now-complete bed area
4. Snuggle/Sleep/Enjoy

Voila!

Thank you to our Ocracoke build for being the guinea pig.

​Model: Mohican
Cost: Starting at $69,000
Exterior Siding: LP Vertical Smart Siding - 60 Year Warranty (With Aluminum Accent Panel)
Roof: Steel Roof - 40 Year Warranty
Exterior Storage Box: Included
Flooring: Luxury Vinyl Plank (LVP) Flooring
Interior Walls: Poplar Tongue & Groove
Hardware Package: Brushed Nickel Hardware Package
Social Area: Custom Bookcase & Open Space for Customer-Provided Furniture
Closet: Custom Shelving & Hanging Clothes Closet
Sleeping: Large King Loft
Stairs: Custom Staircase w/Built-In Storage

Kitchen

Cabinetry: Custom Cabinetry 
Backsplash: None
Countertops: Butcher Block
Sink: 30 In. Stainless Steel Undermount Sink
Oven/Range: None (Customer Provided)
Refrigerator: Apartment-Sized Stainless Steel Refrigerator
Microwave: None (Customer Provided)

Bathroom

Shower: Fiberglass Shower
Toilet: Nature's Head Composting Toilet
Shelving: Floating Shelves
Sink: None
Door: Custom Sliding Barn Door

Water/Heat/Insulation/Power

Heat/AC: Ductless Mini Split
Water Heater: Gas Propane Water Heater (PrecisionTemp)
Electric Service: 50 Amp Service w/Hybrid Power System for Solar
Insulation: Closed Cell Spray Foam Insulation: 3" In Walls/Ceilings, 4" In Floors

Like specifications like these? You can review all of the specs on our homes at www.moderntinyliving.com!
